==Credits and personnel==

Credits are adapted from the liner notes of ''Talk That Talk''.<ref name="Booklet">{{cite album-notes|artist=Rihanna|title=[[Talk That Talk]]|year=2011|format= inlay cover|publisher= [[Def Jam Recordings|Def Jam]], SRP|page=9}}</ref>

;Locations
*Recorded at Roc the Mic Studios and The Jungle City Studios, New York City, New York; Westlake Recording Studios, Los Angeles, California; The Hide Out Studios, London, UK
*Mixed at Ninja Club Studios, Atlanta, Georgia.

;Personnel
{{Div col|cols=2}}
*[[Songwriter|Songwriting]]&nbsp;<U+2013> Ester Dean, Mikkel S. Eriksen, Tor Erik Hermansen, Shawn Carter, Anthony Best, Sean Combs, Chucky Thompson, Christopher Wallace
*[[Record producer|Production]]&nbsp;<U+2013> StarGate
*Recording&nbsp;<U+2013> Mikkel S. Eriksen, Miles Walker, Mike Anderson
*Vocal Production&nbsp;<U+2013> Kuk Harrell
*Vocal Recording&nbsp;<U+2013> Kuk Harrell, Marcos Tovar, Jordan "DJ" Swivel Young
*Mixing&nbsp;<U+2013> Phil Tan
*Mixing assistant&nbsp;<U+2013> Daniela Rivera
*Instrumentation&nbsp;<U+2013> Mikkel S. Eriksen, Tor Erik Hermansen
*Executive producers&nbsp;<U+2013> Tim Blacksmith, Danny D.
